      <!-- Text Block -->
      <div class="about center">
        <p class="project__description">
          At my time so far at University of Washington’s Society for
          Advanced Rocket Propulsion (SARP), I have been apart of two
          major projects. As the Payload Controls team lead, I have
          been in charge of the development of controls systems for
          the various payloads that will be carries aboard the SARP
          2025 launch vehicle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Block -->
      <div class="about center">
        <h3>Drone</h3>
        <p class="project__description">
          While different both projects cover similar objectives containing but
          not limited to the following.
          <ul class="bullets" style="text-align: left;">
            <li>Sensor data gathering, filtering</li>
            <li>Fusing multiple sensors</li>
            <li>PID, LQR, and LQG flight controllers</li>
            <li>Control of hardware devices and control surfaces</li>
            <li>Remote monitoring and control solutions</li>
          </ul>
    
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Block -->
      <section id="projects" class="section projects">
        <div class="projects__grid">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="sarp/img/drop.gif">
